---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Solutions & Services" description="Solving medical scrub manufacturing pain points. Low MOQs, fast lead times, and custom branding for healthcare brands.">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-24">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-black mb-8 text-center italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Solving Your Manufacturing Challenges</h1>
    <p class="text-slate-500 mb-20 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto text-lg italic">At Yilong Scrubs, we don't just take orders; we solve the common "pain points" that healthcare brands face in today’s competitive market.</p>
    
    <div class="space-y-32">
      <!-- Pain Point 1: Low MOQ -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-red-100 text-red-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #1: The "High MOQ" Barrier</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Struggling with excessive minimum order requirements?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">Most factories demand 500+ sets per color, making it impossible for startups or niche clinics to launch their brand without massive inventory risk.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-primary/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-primary shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-primary text-xl mb-4 italic text-primary underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4">Our Solution: Scalable Growth</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed italic">We offer an industry-leading low MOQ starting at just **10 sets per color**. Test the market, grow your collection, and scale at your own pace without the pressure of huge stock levels.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-slate-100">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A33d7ea38935d4a1ba4b7a78911420840r.png" alt="Scalable Low MOQ Solution" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain Point 2: Lead Time -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl bg-slate-100">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A3e81149be9164a8087fe8da73854d6313.png" alt="Fast Sampling & Production" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 text-right lg:text-left">
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-orange-100 text-orange-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #2: The "Slow Response" Trap</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Losing market momentum due to slow lead times?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">In the fast-moving healthcare fashion world, waiting 3 months for production or 2 weeks for a sample kills your brand’s agility.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-secondary/5 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-secondary shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-secondary text-xl mb-4 italic text-secondary underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4">Our Solution: Accelerated Timeline</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-600 italic font-medium">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 lg:justify-start justify-end"><span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> **3-7 Day Sampling**: Idea to prototype in under a week.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 lg:justify-start justify-end"><span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> **15-30 Day Bulk Delivery**: Direct factory-to-door fulfillment.</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 lg:justify-start justify-end"><span class="text-secondary font-bold">✓</span> **24/7 Direct Support**: No middlemen, just Marvin.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Pain Point 3: Quality & Brand Identity -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center mb-32">
        <div>
          <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 font-bold rounded-full text-xs mb-4 uppercase tracking-widest italic">Pain Point #3: Quality & Brand Identity</div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black mb-6 italic text-slate-900 leading-tight">Tired of inconsistent quality or generic products?</h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed italic">If you can't guarantee quality or differentiate your product, you’re forced to compete on price alone. Generic labels won’t build customer loyalty.</p>
          
          <div class="bg-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-3xl border-l-8 border-indigo-600 shadow-sm">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-indigo-600 text-xl mb-4 italic text-indigo-600 underline decoration-2 underline-offset-4">Our Solution: Premium Branding & QC</h4>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed italic">We provide **100% in-house inspection** and a complete branding toolkit: **Private labels**, **custom hangtags**, and **premium packaging** to ensure your brand stands out with top-tier quality.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-square rounded-[3rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
          <img src="https://sc02.alicdn.com/kf/A28f219314e2548f0ba3a87e6f051e6b9o.png" alt="Asian Medical Scrub Quality Control Inspector" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div class="bg-slate-900 text-white rounded-[4rem] p-16 text-center shadow-2xl">
      <h2 class="text-4xl font-black mb-8 italic">Ready to solve your manufacturing headaches?</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12 italic leading-relaxed">Let's discuss how Yilong Scrubs can streamline your production and help you build a profitable medical apparel brand. 20 years of experience is at your service.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="bg-primary px-12 py-5 rounded-full font-black text-xl hover:bg-blue-800 transition shadow-xl uppercase tracking-widest inline-block">Connect with Marvin</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>